M

Matrix - Class in sc.labs.matrices
Matrix class provides an interface for creating matrices of any order which can then be manipulated using other classes such as implementations of the MatrixMultiplier for multiplying matrices.
Matrix(int, int) - Constructor for class sc.labs.matrices.Matrix
Default public constructor.
MatrixMultiplier - Interface in sc.labs.matrices
MatrixMultiplier defines an interface for multiplying Matrix objects.

multiply(Matrix, Matrix) - Method in class sc.labs.matrices.StrassenMultiplier
 
multiply(int[][], int[][]) - Method in class sc.labs.matrices.StrassenMultiplier
Takes two square matrices of order (n x n) where n is a multiple of 2 as two 2D arrays, multiplies them and returns the resulting 2D array.
